# Vue SFC Conventions

## Komponen

- Selalu `<script setup lang="ts">`
- Halaman fitur di `src/components/*.vue`; primitif di `src/components/ui/`
- Composable baru di `src/composables/use*.ts`

## Props & emits

```vue
const props = withDefaults(defineProps<{ isExpanded?: boolean }>(), { isExpanded: true })
const emit = defineEmits<{ navigate: [view: string, data?: unknown] }>()
```

- Hindari nama prop yang bentrok atribut HTML (`isExpanded` bukan `expanded`)
- Props class pakai `className`, bukan `class`

## State

- `ref` / `reactive` / `computed` untuk state lokal
- Jangan tambah Pinia tanpa diminta

## UI kit

- Impor dari `@/components/ui`: Button, Tabs, InputField, SidebarNavigation, dll.
- Button pakai slot `#iconStart` / `#iconEnd`

## Ikon

- Hanya `lucide-vue-next`; dynamic icon via `<component :is="icon" />`

## Map (Leaflet)

- Imperatif di `onMounted`, cleanup di `onUnmounted`
- Import CSS: `leaflet/dist/leaflet.css`, markercluster CSS
- Jangan pakai react-leaflet atau @vue-leaflet

## Sidebar collapsible

- State `sidebarExpanded` di App.vue
- Persist: `localStorage` key `kompak-sidebar-expanded`
- Prop ke SidebarNavigation: `:is-expanded="sidebarExpanded"`
